  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Liebherr built-in lineup we service</h2>
    <p>Liebherr's built-in refrigerator catalog organizes around five main platforms. <b>Monolith integrated column</b> is the ultra-premium integrated series — MRB / MF model prefixes across 24" to 48" widths, full-overlay custom cabinetry panel acceptance, and the deepest European-integration standard in the Liebherr range. <b>CS / CBS side-by-side built-in</b> covers traditional 36" / 42" / 48" side-by-side in stainless or integrated finish, with CS-SBS sub-series for side-by-side-specific configurations that pair refrigerator + freezer as single unit. <b>UIK undercounter integrated</b> covers 24" undercounter refrigerator + freezer drawer installations at kitchen islands, butler's pantries, or secondary-zone refrigeration points. <b>HCB built-in bottom-freezer</b> covers traditional 36" bottom-freezer built-in as single-cabinet alternative. <b>Column-matched freezer units</b> pair with refrigerator columns for matched-column luxury suites (similar architectural pattern to Sub-Zero / Thermador Freedom / Miele MasterCool column-pair suites).</p>
    <p>Every Liebherr built-in integrates BioFresh 0°C humidity-controlled preservation zone (on compatible models) and NoFrost fully-automatic defrost freezer (on freezer-containing units). These signature technologies are service-distinct: BioFresh has its own temperature sensor + humidity damper mechanism requiring dedicated diagnostic path; NoFrost eliminates manual-defrost service items common on legacy non-NoFrost freezers. Parts chain runs through Liebherr USA distribution with typical 5-10 day LA-authorized service lead on common components, 2-3 week on specialty Monolith integration hardware.</p>
  </div></section>

