    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Ice maker module — Liebherr-specific parts</h3><p>Liebherr ice maker module $340–$480; water inlet valve $260–$360. Parts lead time 5-10 day via Liebherr USA distribution.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Door gasket compression loss (European spec)</h3><p>Liebherr European-profile gasket compresses at 10-15 yr → warm temps + cycling. Per-section $300–$440 replacement.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Monolith integrated panel-overlay gasket</h3><p>Full-overlay Monolith integrated units have specific panel-gasket system. $340–$480 replacement; panel-protection discipline during service.</p></div>
